    DeriveTraversable
    DerivingStrategies
    DerivingVia
    DuplicateRecordFields
    EmptyDataDecls
    FlexibleContexts
    FlexibleInstances
    FunctionalDependencies
    GADTs
    GeneralizedNewtypeDeriving
    LambdaCase
    LiberalTypeSynonyms
