    MultiParamTypeClasses
    MultiWayIf
    NamedFieldPuns
    NoFieldSelectors
    NoImplicitPrelude
    NoMonomorphismRestriction
    NumericUnderscores
    OverloadedRecordDot
    OverloadedStrings
    ParallelListComp
    PatternGuards
    QuasiQuotes
    RankNTypes
    RecordWildCards
